Package arcade.agent.cell

Interface Cell

All Superinterfaces:
java.io.Serializable, sim.engine.Steppable
All Known Implementing Classes:
TissueCCell, TissueCell, TissueHCell, TissueSCell
public interface Cell
extends sim.engine.Steppable
A Cell object represents a cell agent.

Types (identifying cell state/phenotype, called type to avoid confusion with simulation state) and flags (identifying cell status) are provided for convenience. Not all implementations of Cell need to utilize all the types or flags. Additional types and flags may be added.

Each Cell implementation has a corresponding code to identify the cell class. Additional codes may be added.

Since:
2.2
Version:
2.3.3
